Mobeti ndembo Neymar Jr. akendaki kotala Pelé na hôpital moko ya Paris epayi wapi mosani oyo ya kala ya football azali kosalisama na infection urinaire. 
 Na photo etiami na Instagram o’mokolo ya lundi, Neymar avandi pene na "djogo" Pelé, bango mibale bazali koseka.
Pelé azali na lopitalo banda mokolo ya mercredi moleki. 
Azali na mibu 78.